Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Classes
  • Deprecated Fields
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    GxExpressions.GxExpressionDatesFormatter
    since version 0.101.0, GxExpressionDatesFormatter is deprecated. Use GxExpressionDateTimesFormatter instead.
    GxFilters.GxFilterDate
    since version 0.101.0, GxFilterDate is deprecated. Use GxFilterBasicDate instead.
  • Deprecated Fields 
    Field and Description
    GxClientModels.GxClientTransactionModel.AddIndex_OBJECT_VARIABLE_SUFFIX_
    `GxClientTransactionModel.addIndex` is deprecated. If you want precision control of adding data, use `BBjGridExWidget.updateData` instead
    GxOptions.GxOptionsDateTime.AllowInput_OBJECT_VARIABLE_SUFFIX_
    since version 0.101.0, GxOptionsDateTime.AllowInput is deprecated. Direct input is always disabled.
    GxOptions.GxOptions.DeltaColumnMode_OBJECT_VARIABLE_SUFFIX_
    use `GxOptions.ImmutableColumns` instead
    GxOptions.GxOptions.EnableFloatingFilter_OBJECT_VARIABLE_SUFFIX_
    enabling/disabling the floatingFilter on the Options level is deprecated. Use `GxColumn.FloatingFilter` on the column level instead.
    GxColumns.GxDefaultColumnGroup.HeaderGroupTooltip_OBJECT_VARIABLE_SUFFIX_
    since version 0.101.0, GxDefaultColumnGroup.HeaderGroupTooltip is deprecated / renamed. Use GxDefaultColumnGroup.HeaderToolTip instead.

    since version 0.101.0, GxOptionsDateTime.setAllowInput(BBjNumber allow!) is deprecated. Direct input is always disabled.

    GxColumns.GxDefaultColumnGroup.setHeaderGroupTooltip(BBjString)

    BBjGridExWidget.BBjGridExWidget.setRowData(BBjNumber, DataRow)
    since version 0.101.0, BBjGridExWidget.setRowData(BBjNumber index!, DataRow row!) is deprecated. Use BBjGridExWidget.updateRow(DataRow row!) instead. The grid can work out the row index by its own
    BBjGridExWidget.BBjGridExWidget.setRowData(DataRow)
    since version 0.101.0, BBjGridExWidget.setRowData(DataRow row!) is deprecated. Use BBjGridExWidget.updateRow(DataRow row!) instead. The grid can work out the row index by its own

    GxFilters.GxFilterSetFilter.setSuppressSyncValuesAfterDataChange(BBjNumber)

    since version 0.101.0, BBjGridExWidget.setVisibleColumn(BBjString columnId!) is deprecated / renamed. Use BBjGridExWidget.ensureColumnVisible(BBjString columnId!) instead.
    BBjGridExWidget.BBjGridExWidget.setVisibleRow(BBjNumber, BBjString)
    since version 0.101.0, BBjGridExWidget.setVisibleRow(BBjNumber index! , BBjString position!) is deprecated / renamed. Use BBjGridExWidget.ensureIndexVisible(BBjNumber index! , BBjString position!) instead.
    BBjGridExWidget.BBjGridExWidget.startNextCellEditing()

    since version 0.101.0, BBjGridExWidget.startPreviousCellEditing() is deprecated / renamed. Use BBjGridExWidget.tabToPreviousCell() instead.
    BBjGridExWidget.BBjGridExWidget.updateRow(BBjNumber, DataRow)
    since version 0.101.0, BBjGridExWidget.updateRow(BBjNumber index!, DataRow row!) is deprecated. Use BBjGridExWidget.updateRow(DataRow row!) instead. The grid can work out the row index by its own
